HEADWORD: Aërofoil
<hw>A"⟦eum⟧r*o*foil`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>A⟦eum⟧ro-</ets> + <ets>foil</ets>.]</ety> <def>A plane or
